ECMO在新冠疫情中扮演上帝？专家：不具备大规模推广条件，并非所有人都适用。
ECMO's Role as God in the New Crown Epidemic Expert: Not all of us have the conditions to do this on a large scale.
张静。
Zhang Jing.
DeepTech深科技                      。
